      <a href="index.html?p=1727#comment-2661"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-06-06T23:32:00-04:00">Friday, June 6, 2008 at 11:32 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This recipe is the absolute best for jam making. You need look no further. I made the most amazing apricot and raspberry jam batches with this last summer. For the raspberry jam, I added a rose geranium leaf to each jar before adding the jam, then canned as usual. Awesome.</p>
    </div>

