    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>By the way: as a lover of cooked bananas, did you ever try banana jam? It&#8217;s delicious. <br />I also like to add a banana to cherry, kiwi or strawberry jam.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?p=1727#comment-2664' data-commentid="2664" data-postid="1727" data-belowelement="comment-2664" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Corrie" aria-label='Reply to Corrie'>Reply</a>    </div>
