    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Kate</cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=1727#comment-2665"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-10-06T05:33:10-04:00">Tuesday, October 6, 2009 at 5:33 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Corrie- I bet a banana curry jam would be amazing&#8230;am I crazy?</p>
<p>I just made this the other night with concord grapes. I followed your method though and it was fabulous&#8230;all of my jars sealed with no problems! To do concord grapes, use a cup of sugar/lb of grapes, peel the grapes and puree peels with sugar. Mix with lemon juice and seeded grape &#8220;pulp&#8221; and boil away!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?p=1727#comment-2665' data-commentid="2665" data-postid="1727" data-belowelement="comment-2665" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Kate" aria-label='Reply to Kate'>Reply</a>    </div>
